PortGroup           github 1.0

github.setup        facebook rocksdb 5.11.3 rocksdb-

revision            1
categories          databases devel
platforms           darwin
license             BSD

maintainers         {stromnov @stromnov} openmaintainer

description         Embedded key-value store for fast storage
